I only expected the room to have a shower, as is often the case in Europe, but was pleasant surprised it has a very good bathroom with a bathtub and a nicely designed jacuzzi that is just right for my sore body and feet after walking several hours along the beautiful streets and canals of the city.	The bathroom has a walk in dresser, and even had a jacuzzi tub and multi jet showers...amenities are by Lush.